        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "刚解决了一个麻烦，可别再出什么新的乱子……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她瞥了我一眼。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你啊……想欺负女孩子也分分时候嘛。",
        "disable": 0
