    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她不知道从哪里摸出来一面小巧的梳妆镜，猛然朝我丢了过来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "凯茜娅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "唇膏还挂着呢，赶紧擦干净。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟瑞斯瞬刻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "——啊！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "满面绯红的瑟瑞斯飞快地瞟了我一眼，然后就别过脸去。凯茜娅则咧着嘴，笑吟吟地盯着我看。",
