        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而自从她沉默地出现之后，我就像是被冰块冻住了一样，挪不动脚步，更掰不开目光。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你看什么。",
        "disable": 0
    },
